Rating: 4
This was a huge hit before our Easter feast; serves 24 appetizer portions in demitasse cups. After reading reviews, I made the following modifications: added 2 Tbsp fresh lemon juice, added an additional 6 oz. chicken broth, upped hot pepper sauce to 3/4 tsp, added 1/8 tsp salt, and 1/4 tsp white pepper. Made this a day ahead, although there was a slight discoloration on top, it easily stirred out. This soup was quite thick and required a spoon. Quick and easy to make if you suddenly find yourself with four ripe avocados.

